ate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">24 July</span> 2018</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Capter+3+It+Only+Takes+A+Spark%3A+The+Hazard+of+Wildfires&amp;rft.pub=Brookings.edu&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.brookings.edu%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F06%2FND-Review-Chapter-3.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3A1997+Indonesian+forest+fires\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation book\">Glover, David (2006). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://books.google.com/books?hl=en&amp;lr=&amp;id=eMBu_rXSq3QC&amp;oi=fnd&amp;pg=PR5&amp;dq=1997+indonesia+forest+fire+causes&amp;ots=IQXaWoxOuq&amp;sig=x0CIVO5azr4Wj0hSzuBBGrdBTSg#v=onepage&amp;q=1997%20indonesia%20forest%20fire%20causes&amp;f=false\"><i>Indonesia's Fires and Haze: The Cost of Catastrophe</i></a>. IDRC. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/9781552503324\" title=\"Special:BookSources/9781552503324\">9781552503324</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Indonesia%27s+Fires+and+Haze%3A+The+Cost+of+Catastrophe&amp;rft.pub=IDRC&amp;rft.date=2006&amp;rft.isbn=9781552503324&amp;rft.aulast=Glover&amp;rft.aufirst=David&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fhl%3Den%26lr%3D%26id%3DeMBu_rXSq3QC%26oi%3Dfnd%26pg%3DPR5%26dq%3D1997%2Bindonesia%2Bforest%2Bfire%2Bcauses%26ots%3DIQXaWoxOuq%26sig%3Dx0CIVO5azr4Wj0hSzuBBGrdBTSg%23v%3Donepage%26q%3D1997%2520indonesia%2520forest%2520fire%2520causes%26f%3Dfalse&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3A1997+Indonesian+forest+fires\" class=\"Z3988\